I was so focused on the test that it took me 2 minutes to realize I was the one singing.

BOY I’M TOO ADDICTED TO THIS SONG!

Buffy/Gryffindor: VERY BOLD and always true to herself (this one is a no brainer)

Andi/ Ravenclaw: CREATIVE, intelligent, practical (always doing what is smart for herself and others)

Jonah/Slytherin: (this one was a bit harder) Leadership, image driven (didn’t want to reveal his problems) CHARISMA

summary: Sooo if Bowie and Bex get married, does Andi’s last name stay? Bex might change to Quinn. And since Bex and Bowie are Andi’s...
body: Sooo if Bowie and Bex get married, does Andi’s last name stay? Bex might change to Quinn. And since Bex and Bowie are Andi’s biological parents (right?), wouldn’t it be complete for Andi to have Bowie’s last name? The Quinn family? Probably not cuz the show is called “Andi Mack”. But I guess the argument can be made that Bex doesn’t have to take Bowie’s last name. But I can see Andi wanting to change her last name cuz she’s like her parents’ number one fan. I can see this last name thing never come up and/or Andi never changes cuz the show is called “Andi Mack”. Or maybe change it to be Andi Mack-Quinn. Maybe this entire last name thing doesn’t matter. 🤷🏾‍♂️
